description.en-us: Haulers was a series of trucks released from 1997 to 2002. This series was produced by ARCO Toys until at least 2000 when any mention of ARCO Toys was dropped from packaging. Some castings were also used in playsets and Super Race Rigs packs. Packaging for this series never featured casting names.
